    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >逆向塔防游戏</h2><br>成为进攻者吧！建立你的军队，引导攻城锤沿着道路穿越障碍和防御工事，攻入敌人城堡。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021860/extras/debbe5ddd02d5fa18a35763684c45d5a.poster.avif?t=1762704822\" width=600 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021860/extras/debbe5ddd02d5fa18a35763684c45d5a.webm?t=1762704822\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021860/extras/debbe5ddd02d5fa18a35763684c45d5a.mp4?t=1762704822\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >不惜一切代价保护攻城锤</h2><br>你的攻城锤是最重要的单位。如果它被摧毁，围攻就结束了。它也是你最强大的单位。引导它穿越敌人城堡，摧毁一路上的每一扇门和障碍。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021860/extras/2faa81f16f485c7a1d0f3cd619e04043.poster.avif?t=1762704822\" width=600 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021860/extras/2faa81f16f485c7a1d0f3cd619e04043.webm?t=1762704822\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021860/extras/2faa81f16f485c7a1d0f3cd619e04043.mp4?t=1762704822\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >召唤旗帜，建立军队，是时候进行围攻了。</h2><br>利用之前攻击的奖励扩充你的军队。从弓箭手、剑士等多种单位中选择，以保护你的攻城锤，为你的王国再夺一个城堡。<br><br><br>使用旗帜系统指挥你的士兵在战场上作战。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021860/extras/81ee0c0223968cc10dd3c5220e35fe56.poster.avif?t=1762704822\" width=600 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021860/extras/81ee0c0223968cc10dd3c5220e35fe56.webm?t=1762704822\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021860/extras/81ee0c0223968cc10dd3c5220e35fe56.mp4?t=1762704822\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >军队全军覆没？立刻行动，成为你天生的国王。</h2><br>用弓箭远程击杀接近的敌人，用剑扫除敌人群体。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021860/extras/7fc3d7b2206f76a1686575a63b870b6a.poster.avif?t=1762704822\" width=600 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021860/extras/7fc3d7b2206f76a1686575a63b870b6a.webm?t=1762704822\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021860/extras/7fc3d7b2206f76a1686575a63b870b6a.mp4?t=1762704822\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >当前功能（更多即将推出）：</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>5个可玩关卡<br></li><li>极简艺术风格<br></li><li>简约策略游戏方式<br></li><li>高分系统</li></ul>",
